                     <interp inst="t18411129-222-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18411129-cd-188" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18411129-222-offence-1 t18411129-cd-188"></join>24th of Novem<lb></lb>ber</rs>, 1 sovereign and 6 half-crowns, the monies of <persName id="t18411129-name-1177" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18411129-name-1177" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
