                        <interp inst="t18411129-name-1180" type="given" value="ELIZABETH"></interp>ELIZABETH NICHOLLS</persName>
                  </hi>. I searched the prisoner at the station, I found a halfpenny in her hand, and she took this sovereign out of her mouth.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I went with my daughter into Stratford; I was not very well; she left me; some strange gentleman came up and asked if I was in distress, and he gave me something which I thought was a shilling; I put it into my mouth, and never took it out till at the station; I did not know it was a sovereign.</p>
